---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Hafiz Farhad, security researcher specializing in cybersecurity, vulnerability research, and digital forensics.">
  <Navigation slot="navigation" />
  
  <div class="space-y-4 other-pages">
    <!-- Header image placeholder - responsive -->
    <div class="mb-6">
      <img
        src="/placeholder.svg?height=45&width=410"
        alt="Hafiz Farhad Header"
        width="410"
        height="45"
        class="w-full h-auto max-w-[410px]"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none">
      <p class="text-sm md:text-xs">
        I'm a security researcher with over a decade of experience in cybersecurity, specializing in vulnerability
        research, digital forensics, and emerging technology security.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm md:text-xs">
        My research focuses on identifying and analyzing security vulnerabilities across various domains including IoT
        devices, mobile applications, AI/ML systems, and cryptographic implementations. I believe in responsible
        disclosure and work closely with vendors to ensure vulnerabilities are properly addressed.
      </p>

      <h2 class="nav-font text-base md:text-sm">Research Areas</h2>
      <ul class="text-sm md:text-xs">
        <li>IoT and embedded systems security</li>
        <li>Mobile application security assessment</li>
        <li>AI/ML security and adversarial attacks</li>
        <li>Cryptographic analysis and implementation</li>
        <li>Digital forensics and incident response</li>
        <li>Network security and penetration testing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="nav-font text-base md:text-sm">Publications & Speaking</h2>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-xs">
        I regularly publish research findings in academic journals and present at security conferences worldwide. My
        work has been featured in leading cybersecurity publications and has contributed to improving the security
        posture of numerous organizations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="nav-font text-base md:text-sm">Contact Information</h2>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-xs">
        <strong>Email:</strong> hafiz@example.com<br />
        <strong>Twitter:</strong> @hafizfarhad<br />
        <strong>LinkedIn:</strong> /in/hafizfarhad<br />
        <strong>GitHub:</strong> /hafizfarhad
      </p>

      <h2 class="nav-font text-base md:text-sm">Certifications</h2>
      <ul class="text-sm md:text-xs">
        <li>CISSP - Certified Information Systems Security Professional</li>
        <li>CEH - Certified Ethical Hacker</li>
        <li>GCIH - GIAC Certified Incident Handler</li>
        <li>OSCP - Offensive Security Certified Professional</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
